      	<figure class="lead-art">
					<div class="aspect-3-2">
                    						<img alt="" src="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo400w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg" width="400" height="267" srcset="https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo400w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg 400w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo800w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg 800w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo1200w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg 1200w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo1600w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg 1600w, https://assets-c3.propublica.org/images/articles/_threeTwo2000w/20190226-uss-fitzgerald-alt-3x2.jpg 2000w" sizes="(min-width: 1720px) 826px, (min-width: 780px) calc(46.09vw + 43px), (min-width: 600px) 59.38vw, 93.21vw"/>
					</div>
											<figcaption class="caption">The USS Fitzgerald on June 17, 2017 after its collision with a cargo ship in the Pacific.
															<span class="credit">(The Asahi Shimbun via Getty Images)</span>
													</figcaption>
									</figure>
            			
			<header class="article-header">

												<div class="series-header">
					<p class="series-title"><a href="https://www.propublica.org/series/navy-accidents-pacific-7th-fleet" aria-label="In the series: Disaster in the Pacific">Disaster in the Pacific</a></p>
									</div>
				
				<h2 class="hed">Navy Promised Changes After Deadly Accidents, but Many Within Doubt It’s Delivering on Them</h2>
								<p class="dek">Interviews and an examination of the Navy’s publicly announced reforms raise uncertainty over whether senior leaders have fully followed through on them after the 7th Fleet disasters in 2017.</p>
								<div class="metadata">
					<p class="byline">by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/robert-faturechi">Robert Faturechi</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/t-christian-miller">T. Christian Miller</a></p>
					<time class="timestamp" datetime="2019-02-26EST04:00">Feb. 26, 2019, 4 a.m. EST</time>
				</div>

								
<nav class="story-tools semi-fixed" data-element-ceiling="body" data-element-floor=".article-wrap">
	<ul>
		<li>
			<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.propublica.org/article/navy-accident-changes-fitzgerald-mccain-davidson" title="Share this story on Facebook">
